---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Level 3: Advanced GEO | Waseem's SEO Guide">
  <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <ol>
      <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="/level2">Level 2</a></li>
      <li aria-current="page">Level 3: Advanced GEO</li>
    </ol>
  </nav>

  <header>
    <span class="badge">LEVEL 3</span>
    <h1>🤖 Advanced GEO Mastery</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Generative Engine Optimization: Making AI Trust & Quote You</p>
    <div class="reading-time-badge">⏱️ ~50 min read</div>
  </header>

  <section class="intro-section">
    <h2>What is GEO?</h2>
    <p>GEO (Generative Engine Optimization) is the art of making your content AI-friendly. As ChatGPT, Claude, and Google SGE become more popular, GEO is becoming essential.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>📚 Topics Covered</h2>
    <ul class="topics-list">
      <li>✓ SEO vs. GEO: The Big Shift</li>
      <li>✓ Pillar 1: Facts Over Fluff</li>
      <li>✓ Pillar 2: Schema for Trust</li>
      <li>✓ Pillar 3: AI-Ready Structure</li>
      <li>✓ Entity Optimization</li>
      <li>✓ E-E-A-T: The Trust Framework</li>
      <li>✓ GEO Audit Checklist</li>
      <li>✓ Knowledge Graph & Entities</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <div class="content-coming-soon">
    <p>🚧 Full content coming soon! This is a preview of the Astro-based structure.</p>
    <p>In the meantime, you can view the <a href="/level1">Level 1 content</a> for a complete example.</p>
  </div>

  <nav class="level-nav">
    <a href="/level2" class="nav-btn">← Level 2: Technical SEO</a>
    <a href="/level4" class="nav-btn">Level 4: Authority & Channels →</a>
  </nav>
</Layout>

<style>
  .breadcrumbs ol {
    display: flex;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .breadcrumbs a {
    color: #667eea;
  }

  header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .badge {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f093fb 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 8px 20px;
    border-radius: 25px;
  }

  .topics-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .topics-list li {
    padding: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .content-coming-soon {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3e0 0%, #ffe0b2 100%);
    border-radius: 15px;
    margin: 40px 0;
  }

  .level-nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }
  .level-nav .nav-btn {
    padding: 12px 24px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f093fb 100%);
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }
</style>
